  "page": "Saffron Straits",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:WorldofIceandFire.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The known world and the location of the Saffron Straits\"><img alt=\"The known world and the location of the Saffron Straits\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/400px-WorldofIceandFire.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/600px-WorldofIceandFire.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/10/WorldofIceandFire.png/800px-WorldofIceandFire.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 92.8%; left: 95.3%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"The known world and the location of the Saffron Straits\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Saffron Straits\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Saffron Straits</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> and the location of the Saffron Straits\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Saffron Straits</b> are the eastern exit of the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>, dividing <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ulthos\" title=\"Ulthos\">Ulthos</a>. The city of <a href=\"/index.php/Asshai\" title=\"Asshai\">Asshai</a> is on the north side of its western entrance. North of the straits are the <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Lands\" title=\"Shadow Lands\">Shadow Lands</a>, and Ulthos is to the south. The Saffron Straits widen to the east, and in them is the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Ulos\" title=\"Ulos\">Ulos</a>;<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> then they run off east outside the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Saffron_Straits&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The Known World.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404125958\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.023 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 614/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12272/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3571/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1962/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 572/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,m